Methods.S:
Two standard procedures were employed to demonstrate HRP 
    with tetramethylbemidine (TMB) as the chromagen (Mesulam, '78; 
    de Olmos et al., '78).

TTE.S:
A much larger labelled fiber 
      contingent than in case RPSI2 ( ventral SI 
      ) reached caudal to the diencephalon .

Discussion.S:
First, the SI appears to be strongly affiliated with the 
    amygdala (see also de Olmos, '72; Schwaber et al., '82; 
    de Olmos et al., '85; Grove, '88).
